                <ul>
                    <li>5–7 million companion animals are given to <span class="text-decoration-underline">animal shelters</span> each year. </li>
                    <li>There are 3,500 <span class="text-decoration-underline">animal shelters</span> in the United States.</li>
                    <li><span class="text-decoration-underline">No-kill shelters</span> can euthanize up to 10% of their animal population. </li>
                    <li>Pet <span class="text-decoration-underline">adoptions have decreased</span> 36% since the COVID-19 pandemic began. </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
